# LinkedIn project description

**AWS EKS DevOps Platform — Personal Portfolio Project**

Designed and implemented an end-to-end DevOps platform for a containerized Python API using AWS, Terraform, Docker, Kubernetes, GitHub Actions, Jenkins, Prometheus, Grafana, and CloudWatch. Built reusable Terraform modules for VPC, EKS, ECR, IAM, and monitoring; implemented CI/CD with testing, security scanning, immutable image publishing, Kubernetes rollout verification, and smoke tests; and added health probes, autoscaling, disruption controls, network policy, dashboards, alerts, and an operations runbook.

Present this honestly as a hands-on personal project. Do not claim it supported real production traffic unless it actually did.
